data.description: TURN KEY!! Beautiful Enchanted Hills home settled on a spacious lot, complete with Hot Tub and landscaped backyard. Main level boasts incredible natural light, guest bedroom, full bath,  and laundry room. Second level reflects large master bedroom, master bath, 2 additional bedrooms, and a full bath. Updates completed: water softener, water heater (within the last 4 years), roof (2 years), carpet (2 years), Inside paint (3 years), outside paint(2 years), floorboards (2 years), master cool evap cooler (2 years), vanity in master bathroom (2 years). RV hookups on side of home and backyard access! Come see this beauty today!
